{
  "text": "The FDR concept reflects the tradeoff between false discoveries and true discoveries in practice, and is connected to minimax estimation theory [CITATION_1] ) and compound decision theory [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . [CITATION_4] showed that, under mild conditions, mFDR = FDR + O(m \u22121/2 ).",
